::Zardus/Oblitertron::

Zardus lands at the entrance of the Alliance base, the Oblitercons seperating 
and landing behind him. Hiss was carrying DevilDuer.

"Hiss, take him to a CR chamber. Dark One, I might need your help with the 
femm you brought in."

Zardus enters the base, Hiss walking off toward the CR chamber and Dark One 
following him. The rest of the Oblitercons walk off toward the CR chambers, 
following Hiss to get healed.
